WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.600
You're too soft. Stay here. Stay on comms.

2
00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:06.160
This kid never gets hot. He's a softie.

3
00:00:09.570 --> 00:00:17.739
Shots are what? I've worked hard for this mission. Can you give me a chance?

4
00:00:18.829 --> 00:00:21.629
I promise you'll get a chance to help me do important things in the future.

5
00:00:22.269 --> 00:00:23.629
Donald wants us to leave soon, boss.

6
00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:38.929
I was wrong. You spared me, boss.

7
00:00:40.420 --> 00:00:47.869
Your face in here, Thomas, though. You want to prove something? Take him out.

8
00:00:48.829 --> 00:00:53.549
Show them you're not to be disrespected. No. No, I've got to stop.

9
00:00:53.549 --> 00:01:01.630
You'll never, never be softie. I was just, I was just shut this. Please don't keep me.

10
00:01:02.350 --> 00:01:09.680
Spread the word. A gusto is to be respected the same as me. If not...

